  <h1><span>July 17, 2004: Remarks on National Security and the War Effort</span>
</h1>


    <div class="share-trigger-mobile"></div>
</div>
<div id="block-mainpagecontent">
  
    
      <article role="article" class="presidential-speech">

  
    

  <div class="ps-container video-container">
    <div class="presidential-speeches--sidebar">
      
<div  class="about-this-episode">
    <h3>About this speech</h3>
      
<div  class="about-this-episode--inner">
      
            <p class="president-name">George W. Bush</p>
      
            <p class="episode-date">July 17, 2004</p>
      
            <div class="about-sidebar--intro"><p>At the George C. Marshall ROTC Award Ceremony in the Virginia Military Institute's Cameron Hall in Lexington, Virginia, President Bush addresses ROTC troops on the current state of national security and the course of the War on Terror&nbsp;looking forward.</p>
</div>
      
  </div>
  </div>
    </div>

    <div class="presidential-speeches--body-wrapper">
     <a href="/the-presidency/presidential-speeches" class="back-to-listing--cta">Presidential Speeches</a> <span class="nav-separator">|</span> <label class="presidential-speeches--label">George W. Bush Presidency</label>
      <h2 class="presidential-speeches--title"><span>July 17, 2004: Remarks on National Security and the War Effort</span>
</h2>
      
<div  class="presidential-speeches--body">
      <div class="video-parent">
	<div class="video-container">
